      <title>英国电网投资计划将推高消费者电费</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/uk-grid-investment-plans-set-to-drive-up-bills-for-consumers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国公用事业公司预计将在五年内投资超过 770 亿英镑（980 亿美元）用于升级电网，这将增加消费者的负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/uk-grid-investment-plans-set-to-drive-up-bills-for-consumers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 14:12:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Taconic 退出商业地产领域，部门主管加入 Axonic</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/taconic-exits-commercial-real-estate-unit-head-to-join-axonic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Taconic Capital Advisors 正在逐步结束其商业房地产业务，并正在就将该部门的一只基金出售给 Axonic Capital 进行深入谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/taconic-exits-commercial-real-estate-unit-head-to-join-axonic</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 13:45:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>德国要求裕信银行出售其持有的德国商业银行股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/germany-says-it-expects-unicredit-to-sell-commerzbank-stake</link>
      <description><![CDATA[就在意大利联合信贷银行宣布增持德国商业银行股份数小时后，德国又要求联合信贷银行出售其持有的德国商业银行股份，这进一步加剧了这家德国银行两大股东之间的紧张关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/germany-says-it-expects-unicredit-to-sell-commerzbank-stake</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 13:41:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹麦警告俄罗斯可能派遣军舰护送油轮</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/denmark-warns-russia-may-send-warships-to-escort-oil-tankers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[丹麦警告称，俄罗斯海军可能开始护送所谓的影子舰队油轮通过丹麦海峡，以升级对北约国家的挑衅。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-18/denmark-warns-russia-may-send-warships-to-escort-oil-tankers</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 18 Dec 2024 13:33:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
